1. *Plaćam* račune u roku. (I pay the bills on time.)
2. Tvoja devojka *plaća* skupu odeću. (Your girlfriend pays for expensive clothes.)
3. *Plaćao* sam za večeru. (I paid for dinner.)
4. *Plaćamo* za naše usluge. (We are paying for our services.)
5. *Plaćanje* je uspešno završeno. (The payment was successful.)